Idris Elba is a man of many talents. The actor and musician recently teamed up with Wiley, Sean Paul and Stefflon Don for a new song “Boasty” and the video has been released as well. Boasty features a young Wiley played by child-actor Brooklyn Appiah and follows each artist as they fight for screen time and command our attention for their bars. It was directed by Henry Scholfield and shot in London. Watch it below 